## CIQL Documentation for deployment (production)

### Prerequises
- [Nodejs](https://nodejs.org/en/)
- [PostreSQL](https://www.postgresql.org)
- [Redis BD](https://redis.io/)
- [PM2](https://pm2.keymetrics.io/docs/usage/quick-start/)

### Databases supported
- [PostreSQL](https://www.prisma.io/docs/concepts/database-connectors/postgresql)
- [Microsoft SQL Server](https://www.prisma.io/docs/concepts/database-connectors/sql-server)
- [Mysql](https://www.prisma.io/docs/concepts/database-connectors/mysql)
- [Sqlite](https://www.prisma.io/docs/concepts/database-connectors/sqlite)
- [MongoDB](https://www.mongodb.com/)

### For deployment

1. In **.env** define your prod database information
2. Following your database type change datasource/provider in **prisma/schema.prisma** (postgresql, mysql, sqlite, sqlserver, mongodb)
3. Type **yarn install** for installing all node packages
4. Type **yarn start** to run project